=======================================================================

This repository is provided as a source-available academic demonstration
associated with the research paper "An Offline-First Android System for
Operational Analysis of Grape Bunches via On-Device Inference and Multi-View
A/B Fusion". It is intended for review, reproducibility, and non-commercial
academic evaluation only.

The public version is local-only: backend services, cloud synchronization,
remote storage, user authentication, and credential-based login are disabled.
No username or password is required in the public demo build.

Commercial use, production deployment, and commercial redistribution require
prior written permission from the authors. Academic use should cite the
associated research paper.

